start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":36,"title":"","content":"<p><strong>The brand is dedicated to sustainability and ethical practices, and works hard to ensure that its materials are sourced from sustainable and ethical sources.<\/strong><\/p><p><\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1d3b4a","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":""}}},"block_order":["template--16607580291326__1a06ebb0-5ccf-441d-a7aa-94e9eeebbfd0-1669799937bc5ef203-0"],"settings":{"full_width":false,"enable_parallax":true,"spacing":"small"}},"0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-0":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_1.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":false,"rating":4,"author":"Phase 1","title":"Inception","content":"<p>Doeraa was founded by a group of fashion-conscious individuals who wanted to create a brand that would empower consumers to make a positive impact on the world through their fashion choices.<\/p>"}},"template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-1":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_2_11e1bb2d-147f-4801-937f-1f5df4c099df.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":false,"rating":5,"author":"Phase 2","title":"Early days","content":"<p>In the early days, Doeraa focused on sourcing sustainable materials and working with skilled artisans to create a range of stylish and functional fashion products that were made with the consumer in mind.<\/p>"}},"template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-2":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_3.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":false,"rating":4,"author":"Phase 3","title":"Growth and expansion","content":"<p>As Doeraa gained popularity among fashion-conscious consumers, the brand expanded its offerings to include a wider range of products and began collaborating with more artisans from around the world.<\/p>"}},"96fa7aa9-e4dc-4520-8205-193af3ca1e24":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_4.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":false,"rating":4,"author":"Phase 4","title":"Commitment to sustainability","content":"<p>Doeraa became known for its commitment to sustainability, and the brand implemented various initiatives to reduce its environmental impact and support ethical and sustainable practices in the production of its fashion products.<br\/><br\/><\/p>"}},"8585f11d-0951-46eb-81b2-d8c0b6bdeae5":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_5.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":false,"rating":4,"author":"Phase 5","title":"Giving back","content":"<p>In addition to its focus on sustainability, Doeraa also made a commitment to giving back to the community, and began donating a portion of its profits to charitable causes around the world. Today, Doeraa is a well-respected fashion brand that is known for its commitment to sustainability, social responsibility, and creating products that are not only stylish, but also have a positive impact on the world.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-0","template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-1","template--16607580291326__0d2dc456-3818-4b40-8314-8f2712adcf29-166980000208fece27-2","96fa7aa9-e4dc-4520-8205-193af3ca1e24","8585f11d-0951-46eb-81b2-d8c0b6bdeae5"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"stack_testimonials":false,"subheading":"","title":"Our Journey","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"","background":"","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","heading_color":"","heading_gradient":"","testimonial_card_background":"","testimonial_card_text_color":""}}},"order":["main","0f203ba0-5903-436d-8681-74cae8df2